Bonekickers 

Tue 22 Jul, 21:00 - 22:00 60 mins 

3/6. The Eternal Fire

While exploring the high-risk secret Celtic chambers beneath the Roman Baths, the ancient and tragic tale of Celtic Warrior Queen Boudicca, and Roman soldier Quintanus, is unravelled by Gillian and Ben who confront their own past relationship.
